This sub-sample has been obtained by ﬁrstly classifying the FCCs as low-capital-intensity companies if they fall within the ﬁrst quintile of the sample distribution based on the average value of capital intensity shown during the sample period. 
Then DCCs that fall in the same quintile have been selected. 
The analysis has been conducted by size categories, deﬁned in terms of total sales. 
